<br>
Redo Mend Companion to a one hour refresh and have Hasten Mend reduce time on top of this by 20% / 40% / 60% (instead of the current 10/20/30) and you don't even need a spell.<br>
<br>
My problem with a spell as opposed to an AA is that with current (and upcoming PoP) AA/FT/KEI mana just isn't meaningful anymore. Give me any spell at all and unless its ridiculously expensive ( and I mean 1000 mana or so) then you can cast it all day long. I spam Transons at will now and don't notice the mana cost. MC3 + KEI + Transons + FT3 and your regening the cost of the heal in 60-90 seconds.<br>
<br>
Problem with a 1600-2000 point heal, be it HoT or normal, is that epic mages would become retardedly overpowered. Even non-epic mages wouldn't be far behind. Redoing Mend Companion would keep some form of cap on the situation via its refresh rate whilst still allowing us to either save our pets in extremis or refresh their HP every so often. <p><a href=http://www.afflictionguild.com/profile.php?username=Zaniel&charactername=Zaniel>Zaniel Stormseeker</a><br><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>60th Arch Mage</a><br><a href=http://www.afflictionguild.com>Affliction</a><br><SELECT>
